696
00:47:59,200 --> 00:48:00,480
Bila-bila masa anda mahukannya…

697
00:48:07,160 --> 00:48:08,160
Saya sentiasa bersedia.

698
00:48:12,920 --> 00:48:17,160
Kalau kita buat satu lagi masa,
